me hot gedarft grobn,

00:25:27.177 --> 00:25:29.180
nayntsik tsentimeter tif

00:25:29.523 --> 00:25:31.222
yarikes, shantsn.

00:25:32.004 --> 00:25:34.310
un ahin araynleygn ⟨karbenen⟩.

00:25:34.720 --> 00:25:36.841
s'iz geven zeyer a shvere arbet.

00:25:37.319 --> 00:25:39.490
di ⟨karbenen⟩ zenen geven mit blay,

00:25:39.732 --> 00:25:41.431
dik, shver,

00:25:41.605 --> 00:25:45.262
deys hot men gedarft shlepn oyf di akslen ven me hot shoyn gemakht di yarikes,

00:25:45.672 --> 00:25:46.629
un deys,

00:25:46.786 --> 00:25:51.640
un un tsu arbetn in droysn, un do hot geshaynt di zun, un do hot geregnt.

00:25:54.363 --> 00:25:56.197
un me hot gearbet

00:25:56.287 --> 00:25:58.374
fun ven me iz ongekumen ahin,

00:25:58.480 --> 00:26:01.006
biz um tsvelefe tsayt, un tsvelefe

00:26:01.130 --> 00:26:04.013
fleg men bakumen a halbe liter zup,

00:26:04.013 --> 00:26:06.187
me hot es gerufn di Buna zup.

00:26:07.154 --> 00:26:09.241
dos hot men es gerufn, vi a nomen.

00:26:09.922 --> 00:26:11.755
un der nokh vayter arbetn,

00:26:11.964 --> 00:26:13.426
biz far nakhts,

00:26:14.934 --> 00:26:17.255
biz me hot undz vayter tsuzamengenumen,

00:26:16.867 --> 00:26:18.540
vos iz geven di zup?

00:26:19.422 --> 00:26:20.311
di zup,

00:26:20.570 --> 00:26:25.104
hot men gehat mazl az se ge- ge- geshvumen a por bletlekh derin.

00:26:25.784 --> 00:26:29.882
dos iz es geven der vos hot gehat mazl un se geshvumen a por breklekh derin, se nisht geven vaser

00:26:29.882 --> 00:26:33.389
epes, ikh veys nisht, vos iz geven oysgekokht derin.

00:26:33.699 --> 00:26:37.152
keyn keyn makeronen un keyn fleysh iz nisht geven derin.

00:26:38.457 --> 00:26:43.717
ober s'iz geven gants a, a mol iz es geven gedekhter un a mol iz es ge- geven reyn vaser.

00:26:45.663 --> 00:26:48.678
un dortn iz geven zeyer shver di arbet un

00:26:49.224 --> 00:26:55.074
nokh etlekhe vokhn hob ikh gezen az do vet es nisht, ikh bin geven mit a khaver tsuzamen, vos ikh darf oykhet ervenen,

00:26:56.142 --> 00:26:58.617
fun der fabrik vos ikh hob gearbet, der Sheyner,

00:26:58.690 --> 00:27:02.650
iz dos yingl zay- fun Shayner, Yankl,

00:27:02.791 --> 00:27:05.334
iz geven mayn a khaver fun kindvayz oys.

00:27:05.660 --> 00:27:10.700
un me hot zikh tsuzamengehaltn ⟨tsveynem⟩ oyfn, tsuzamen gelegn un tsuzamen gegangen di gantse tsayt.

00:27:12.190 --> 00:27:13.096
un

00:27:13.186 --> 00:27:19.731
er hot es leyder nisht ibergelebt. er iz nokh tsvey dray monat iz er avekgefaln. er iz geven geven a shvakher yingl fun mir.

00:27:19.750 --> 00:27:24.065
ikh bin geven efsher fizish shtarker geboyt vi er.

00:27:24.290 --> 00:27:26.934
un me hot zikh tsuzamengehaltn un me hot ge- diskutirt,

00:27:26.990 --> 00:27:28.739
vos vet zayn mit undz.

00:27:28.930 --> 00:27:30.224
vos vet vern.

00:27:31.377 --> 00:27:38.952
un azoy, un far nakhts arayngekumen tsu der arbet hot men nokh a mol bakumen epes tsu esn a bisl, demolts iz shoyn geven oykhet a zup, gedekhter.

00:27:38.952 --> 00:27:41.581
oykhet nokh a sho anderthalbn apel,

00:27:42.768 --> 00:27:49.664
shteyn in droysn in regn un in di zun. un v- ver s'iz avekgefaln iz shoyn ave- hot men nisht oy- oyfgeshtelt.

00:27:50.935 --> 00:27:53.059
vos hot men nokh gekent tun a sakh mol,

00:27:53.062 --> 00:27:56.887
tomer hot men gezen eyner fun di khaveyrim heybt on zikh shoyn tsu shoklen, hot men im

00:27:57.179 --> 00:28:01.477
tsugeshtelt an aksl, oyb oy- oy- oyb der der der der

00:28:01.600 --> 00:28:05.662
S. S. hobn es nisht gezen az me me halt im unter un azoy vayter.

00:28:07.456 --> 00:28:08.682
un

00:28:09.110 --> 00:28:12.395
oyf der nakht hot men nokh a mol bakumen a a zup,

00:28:13.497 --> 00:28:19.989
un deys iz es geven un nokh dem hot men zikh gevashn un un un un zikh leygn, me iz zikh avekgefaln fun di fis yedn tog.

00:28:20.467 --> 00:28:22.840
veynik esn un shver arbetn.

00:28:23.133 --> 00:28:26.958
un me iz fun tog tsu tog shvakher gevorn.

00:28:27.689 --> 00:28:29.844
s'iz nokh geven fun tsvishn

00:28:30.102 --> 00:28:31.728
shteterishe mentshn,

00:28:31.728 --> 00:28:35.919
zenen geven elter. ikh bin geven tsvontsik yor, zenen geven shoyn draysik, fertsik yor.

00:28:36.177 --> 00:28:39.429
zey hobn undz nokh getreyst a bisl un un

00:28:39.738 --> 00:28:44.643
un gehaltn in dermuntern undz a bisl, me zol zikh nisht farlozn un azoy vayter.

00:28:45.290 --> 00:28:47.056
ober laykht iz es nisht geven.

00:28:49.120 --> 00:28:50.819
nokh etlekhe vokhn,

00:28:52.158 --> 00:28:54.130
bay der arbet in droysn,

00:28:54.130 --> 00:28:57.586
vos hot efsher ge- mitgeholfn a sakh baym geblibn lebn,

00:28:59.161 --> 00:29:00.877
iz der kapto Vili,

00:29:01.135 --> 00:29:03.475
kapo Vili iz gekumen a mol un er hot

00:29:04.443 --> 00:29:07.171
gezogt er darf hobn tishlers, tsvey tishlers.

00:29:08.560 --> 00:29:10.782
keyn tishler bin ikh keyn mol nisht geven,

00:29:11.362 --> 00:29:14.022
ober ikh hob mir gemakht dem kheshbn,

00:29:15.091 --> 00:29:18.123
keyn mer ven dokh gornisht darfn boyen,

00:29:20.474 --> 00:29:22.016
vos ken shoyn do zayn?

00:29:22.027 --> 00:29:23.827
erger vi ikh hob hitster

00:29:24.423 --> 00:29:27.016
vet es nisht zayn, un me iz shoyn geven fartsveyflt.

00:29:27.545 --> 00:29:28.453
me hot geklert,

00:29:28.490 --> 00:29:31.488
zayn vos vet zayn, zen efsher ken men epes beser

00:29:32.034 --> 00:29:34.981
makht a poyze do, vayl vayl me darf UNK

00:29:32.135 --> 00:29:33.328
makhn.

00:29:36.202 --> 00:29:37.834
tsu vern shlus.
